+ * mc_get_version() - Retrieves the Management Complex firmware
+ *			version information
+ * @mc_io:		Pointer to opaque I/O object
+ * @cmd_flags:		Command flags; one or more of 'MC_CMD_FLAG_'
+ * @mc_ver_info:	Returned version information structure
+ *
